<div id="acknowledgments">

<h3>Acknowledgments</h3>

<p>
Thanks to Andrea Pitts, who helped me conceptualize parts of an early
draft of the entry and who, alongside PJ DiPietro, provided feedback
on an early version of Section 2. Thanks also to Talia Bettcher and
Amy Marvin who provided comments on the whole. Thanks to Ann Garry and
Cheshire Calhoun for making the entry more accessible. Thanks also to
the trans and gender disruptive people, and allies and friends, with
whom I have thought many of these things through. Thanks also to Talia
and Jake, for their friendship and for leading the way.</p>
